gitudinal waves and shear waves.\nFor the numerical solution of these equations, an efficient numerical method\nbased on a staggered-grid finite difference scheme is used. The results of\nsolving some numerical test problems are presented and discussed\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2019 19:18:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2020 16:42:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-11"}
