 transport. Our findings\nindicate that the collective neutrino oscillation may occur more commonly in\nCCSNe and suggest that the CCSN community needs to accommodate these\noscillations self-consistently in the modelling of CCSNe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2019 22:53:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
